{"tid":1253974,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《捉猴啦》註冊了全新推特賬號慶祝系列誕生20週年，或將推出新作","createTime":"2019-06-24T01:04:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T12:43:28.000Z","uid":75050,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fd403b1d566ffda93b43e1462ea57e08c9680f3e","tid":1253974,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:04:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2365606723709835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2365606723709835&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr10zKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=5555c99b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2365606723709835</a><br />\n<br />\n【業界】《捉猴啦》系列或將推出新作<br />\n<br />\n  Sony本月為旗下經典作品《捉猴啦》（Ape Escape）註冊了全新推特賬號@piposaru20th，此賬號發表的第一條推特就是慶祝《捉猴啦》系列誕生20週年，並配文稱&ldquo;一直在逃來逃去，已經不會再有人追來了吧&hellip;&hellip;？&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n  此外Sony還在PlayStation官網上線了本作的紀念頁面。突如其來的一系列動作讓不少玩家猜測《捉猴啦》系列或將推出新作。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCnwmhE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCnwmhE.png&h=a2669db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PwKR5Kk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPwKR5Kk.png&h=f61012d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64f14486abb5bac833465d67f425c766cc4e4398","tid":1253974,"uid":66113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"816af59d745f507aa3e2b818db998ea0382dfb83","tid":1253974,"uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"64f14486abb5bac833465d67f425c766cc4e4398","tid":1253974,"uid":66113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T01:19:40.000Z","msg":"有消息好過無消息<img src=\"/assets/faces